computedFields.name: ValueUnreceivedUnvoucheredAmount
computedFields.saqlExpression:
case when SCMC__Quantity_Received__c > 'SCMC__Quantity_Vouchered__c' then 
	case when SCMC__Total_Cost__c - ('SCMC__Unit_Cost_With_Options__c' * 'SCMC__Quantity_Received__c') > 0 then
		SCMC__Total_Cost__c - ('SCMC__Unit_Cost_With_Options__c' * 'SCMC__Quantity_Received__c')
	else 0
	end
else 
	case when SCMC__Total_Cost__c - ('SCMC__Unit_Cost_With_Options__c' * 'SCMC__Quantity_Vouchered__c') > 0 then
		SCMC__Total_Cost__c - ('SCMC__Unit_Cost_With_Options__c' * 'SCMC__Quantity_Vouchered__c')
	else 0
	end
end

computedFields.name: PeriodNameDate
computedFields.saqlExpression: toDate(case when c2g_PeriodNumber_c_as_number < 1 then 'Year.Name'+"01" when c2g_PeriodNumber_c_as_number == 101 then number_to_string('c2g_Year_c_as_number'+ 1, "####") +"01" when c2g_PeriodNumber_c_as_number > 12 then 'Year.Name'+"12" else 'Year.Name' + substr('c2g__PeriodNumber__c', 2) end, "yyyyMM")
computedFields.label: Financial Year-Period (s)

expression.saqlExpression: case when 'MatchingLineId' is null && previous('MatchingLineId') is not null then "False" else "True" end

computedFields.name: Churn
computedFields.saqlExpression: case when 'ContractLineItemFfbcEndDate' is not null && 'NextContractLineItemId' == "Unknown" && 'ContractFfbcStatus' != "Superseded" && 'SystemNextOpportunityProcessAction' != "Existing Customer - Replacement" then -'ValueContractLineItemFfbcMonthlyRecurringRevenue' end
computedFields.label: MRR Churn

computedFields.name: ContractAdjustmentsReplaced
computedFields.saqlExpression: case when 'SystemNextOpportunityProcessAction' == "Existing Customer - Replacement" then -'ValueContractLineItemFfbcMonthlyRecurringRevenue' end
computedFields.label: MRR Contract Adjustments Replaced

computedFields.name: ContractAdjustmentsReplacement
computedFields.saqlExpression: case when 'SystemProcessAction' == "Existing Customer - Replacement" && 'ContractFfbcStatus' != "Superseded" then 'ValueContractLineItemFfbcMonthlyRecurringRevenue' end
computedFields.label: MRR Contract Adjustments Replacement

computedFields.name: DownSell
computedFields.saqlExpression: case when 'PreviousContractLineItemId' != "Unknown" && 'SystemProcessAction' != "Existing Customer - Upgrade" && 'ValueContractLineItemFfbcMonthlyRecurringRevenue' < 'ValueTotalPreviousMonthlyRecurringRevenue' then 'ValueContractLineItemFfbcMonthlyRecurringRevenue' - 'ValueTotalPreviousMonthlyRecurringRevenue' end
computedFields.label: MRR Down Sell

computedFields.name: NetNew
computedFields.saqlExpression: case when 'SystemProcessAction' == "New Customer" && 'ContractFfbcStatus' != "Superseded" then case when  'PreviousContractLineItemId' != "Unknown" then 'ValueTotalPreviousMonthlyRecurringRevenue' else 'ValueContractLineItemFfbcMonthlyRecurringRevenue' end end
computedFields.label: MRR Net New

computedFields.name: RenewalGap
computedFields.saqlExpression: case when 'SystemProcessAction' == "Existing Customer - Renewal" && 'ContractLineItemFfbcPreviousContractLineItemId' != "Unknown" then daysBetween(toDate('RenewedContractLineItemFfbcEndDate', "yyyy-MM-dd"), toDate('ContractLineItemFfbcStartDate', "yyyy-MM-dd")) - 1 when 'SystemNextOpportunityProcessAction' == "Existing Customer - Renewal" && 'NextContractLineItemId' != "Unknown" then daysBetween(toDate('ContractLineItemFfbcEndDate', "yyyy-MM-dd"), toDate('NextContractLineItemFfbcStartDate', "yyyy-MM-dd")) - 1 end
computedFields.label: Renewal Gap

computedFields.name: Renewals
computedFields.saqlExpression: case when 'PreviousContractLineItemId' != "Unknown" && 'SystemProcessAction' == "Existing Customer - Renewal" then case when 'ValueContractLineItemFfbcMonthlyRecurringRevenue' > 'ValueTotalPreviousMonthlyRecurringRevenue' then 'ValueTotalPreviousMonthlyRecurringRevenue' else 'ValueContractLineItemFfbcMonthlyRecurringRevenue' end end
computedFields.label: MRR Renewals

computedFields.name: ReplacementDate
computedFields.saqlExpression: case when 'SystemNextOpportunityProcessAction' == "Existing Customer - Replacement" && 'ContractLineItemFfbcEndDate' is not null then toDate('ContractLineItemFfbcEndDate_sec_epoch' + 86400) end
computedFields.label: Replacement Date

computedFields.name: Upsell
computedFields.saqlExpression: case when 'SystemProcessAction' == "Existing Customer - Upgrade" then 'ValueContractLineItemFfbcMonthlyRecurringRevenue' when 'PreviousContractLineItemId' != "Unknown" && 'ValueContractLineItemFfbcMonthlyRecurringRevenue' > 'ValueTotalPreviousMonthlyRecurringRevenue' then 'ValueContractLineItemFfbcMonthlyRecurringRevenue' - 'ValueTotalPreviousMonthlyRecurringRevenue' end
computedFields.label: MRR Upsell

computedFields.name: c2g_Period_c_as_special
computedFields.saqlExpression: case when 'c2g__PeriodNumber__c' == "000" then "True" when 'c2g__PeriodNumber__c' == "100" then "True" when 'c2g__PeriodNumber__c' == "101" then "True" else "False" end

computedFields.name: Quarter
computedFields.saqlExpression: case when 'c2g__PeriodNumber__c' <= "003" then "Q1" when 'c2g__PeriodNumber__c' <= "006" then "Q2" when 'c2g__PeriodNumber__c' <= "009" then "Q3" when 'c2g__PeriodNumber__c' <= "012" then  "Q4" when 'c2g__PeriodNumber__c' == "100" then "[100]" when 'c2g__PeriodNumber__c' == "101" then "[101]" else 'c2g__PeriodNumber__c' end

computedFields.name: DaysInPeriod
computedFields.saqlExpression: daysBetween(toDate('c2g__StartDate__c',"yyyy-MM-dd"), toDate('c2g__EndDate__c',"yyyy-MM-dd")) + case when c2g__PeriodNumber__c == "000" || 'c2g__PeriodNumber__c' == "100" || 'c2g__PeriodNumber__c' == "101" then 0 else 1 end
computedFields.label: Number of Days in Period
